Once we’re out,

86
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:38,260
burn the gates immediately.

87
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:40,320
In the meantime, Yujiang, Xianwan,

88
00:04:40,490 --> 00:04:42,240
you two set all posts in the city on fire

89
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,610
