100
00:05:02,490 --> 00:05:04,050
His only son left is in danger.

101
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,110
It’s do-or-die.

102
00:05:07,170 --> 00:05:09,140
I expect your full cooperation.

103
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:10,170
Whatever it takes,

104
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:11,670
we cannot lose the last one

105
00:05:11,670 --> 00:05:12,850
to carry on Marquis’s bloodline.

106
00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:14,470
Aye. Consider it done.

107
