in vain.

114
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,000
Here comes the devil.

115
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:46,790
Move!

116
00:05:52,110 --> 00:05:53,790
Young Master, this…

117
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:54,420
This…

118
00:05:54,670 --> 00:05:55,410
Open the door.

119
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,470
Your Excellency Yan, you’re a lucky man.

120
00:06:05,470 --> 00:06:07,400
Even in prison,

121
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,980
there’s a beauty around you

122
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:11,900
and you still got visitors.

123
00:06:12,810 --> 00:06:13,870
What are you doing here?

124
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,660
I am checking up on you.

125
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:16,990
We are friends.

126
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:18,250
Now you are in trouble,

127
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:20,010
I should pay you a visit.

128
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:25,350
What’s that look?

129
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,220
Do you hate me?

130
00:06:27,730 --> 00:06:29,200
Why?

131
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,790
I only killed

132
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:32,320
your pregnant sister.

133
00:06:32,810 --> 00:06:34,680
Compared with Yuwen Huai
who killed your father,

134
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,300
Wei Guang who planned the massacre,

135
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:38,870
and Yuwen Yue who shot you,

136
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:40,240
I’m merciful.

137
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:41,330
What’s the matter?

138
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,620
You still don’t know?

139
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:44,510
You really thought His Majesty

140
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:46,430
killed your father for no reason?

141
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:48,630
He had ordered Yuwen Yue to collect

142
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:50,080
information about your family

143
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,870
through the Eye of Intel a long time ago.

144
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:53,470
You probably don’t know

145
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,680
that your best friend

146
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,770
was aware of that long ago,

147
00:06:56,770 --> 00:06:57,750
but chose not to tell you.

148
00:06:58,250 --> 00:06:59,020
They are the ones

149
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:01,010
who are sending you to hell.

150
00:07:02,530 --> 00:07:03,840
You’re lying!

151
00:07:04,570 --> 00:07:06,880
That day,
you were already out of the city,

152
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:09,080
but got shot in the end, right?

153
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,380
It was him.

154
00:07:13,290 --> 00:07:14,830
He deliberately spread the words

155
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:17,150
across the entire city.

156
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,830
Even His Majesty

157
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,350
spoke highly of him.

158
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:23,810
All our lives belong to His Majesty.

159
00:07:23,810 --> 00:07:26,380
Yan Xun,
there was nothing personal between us.

160
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:28,510
But your family was too unfortunate.

161
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:31,030
Blame yourself

162
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:33,120
for getting on my nerves.

163
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,690
I have experienced more

164
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:36,850
than you could imagine

165
00:07:37,180 --> 00:07:41,070
but I don’t accept failure.

166
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:44,710
I won’t kill you today.

167
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:46,120
You like this girl,

168
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,290
right?

169
00:07:47,490 --> 00:07:48,600
I will cut off

170
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,850
all her fingers.

171
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:52,010
Let’s see if you still like her then.

172
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,730
I dare you!

173
00:07:57,410 --> 00:07:58,100
Go!

174
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:03,160
Achu!

175
00:08:08,370 --> 00:08:09,260
Stop!

176
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,150
Don’t move.

177
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,700
Behave yourself.

178
00:08:29,170 --> 00:08:30,110
Let go of her!

179
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:33,160
Bitch!

180
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:35,010
Do you remember what you owe me?

181
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:38,640
Zhao Xifeng,

182
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:41,560
I will kill you!

183
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:44,280
Excuse me?

184
00:08:44,620 --> 00:08:45,880
Right now, even a stray dog

185
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,640
is better than you.

186
00:08:48,490 --> 00:08:50,480
Your life is at my fingertips.

187
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,750
You want to kill me?

188
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:53,050
Do it to me!

189
00:08:56,370 --> 00:08:57,810
You’re a piece of trash.

190
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,940
Someone

191
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:02,250
will kill you for me.

192
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:04,620
All I need is a few fingers.

193
00:09:06,730 --> 00:09:09,180
Take mine instead.

194
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:12,370
Take mine!

195
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,810
Look at you two lovebirds.

196
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:16,800
We’re friends.

197
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,930
If you want to play the hero,

198
00:09:17,930 --> 00:09:19,180
I’ll certainly allow it.

199
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,450
Cut them off yourself.

200
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:32,960
Yan Xun.

201
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:34,570
No, Yan Xun!

202
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:36,350
Do it now!

203
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:39,840
Let go of her.

204
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:43,280
Give them back.

205
00:09:43,860 --> 00:09:44,670
Yan Xun.

206
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,450
Don’t do it!

207
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:54,010
Yan Xun!

208
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,770
Yan Xun!

209
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:57,990
Have you forgotten

210
00:09:57,990 --> 00:09:59,150
