211
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,370
Don’t do it. No!

212
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:02,860
Do it.

213
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:03,560
No.

214
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,740
I am not worth it.

215
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,000
Don’t do it!

216
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:08,620
Don’t!

217
00:10:08,620 --> 00:10:09,420
Yan Xun!

218
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:11,140
You are definitely worth it.

219
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,070
You mean

220
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:16,020
the world to me.

221
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,080
Yan Xun!

222
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:28,660
Yan Xun!

223
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,020
Let go of me!

224
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:51,610
Yan Xun.

225
00:10:51,930 --> 00:10:53,140
Zhao Xifeng.

226
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,330
Are you satisfied now?

227
00:10:55,710 --> 00:10:57,030
Not yet.

228
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,720
I want your hand,

229
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,020
but you only cut off one finger.

230
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:02,160
Are you kidding me?

231
00:11:03,090 --> 00:11:04,260
I will kill you!

232
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,210
Achu!

233
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:11,940
= Imperial Prison =

234
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:21,400
Zhong Yu, Cavalrymen

235
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,220
