236
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,940
We’d better leave now.

237
00:11:24,420 --> 00:11:25,770
If we all die,

238
00:11:25,770 --> 00:11:27,230
no one will be able to help His Excellency.

239
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:28,100
Retreat!

240
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,530
Retreat. Retreat.

241
