246
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:52,010
We can’t defeat them.

247
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:53,460
You should leave through the back door.

248
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:56,960
Let’s go.

249
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:36,890
Achu.

250
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,280
Don’t cry.

251
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,800
I’m fine.

252
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:47,230
Without that finger,

253
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,550
how could you hold your sword?

254
00:12:53,420 --> 00:12:54,330
How could you…

255
00:12:55,770 --> 00:12:57,430
How could you shoot again?

256
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:04,020
See,

257
00:13:05,450 --> 00:13:06,940
I only cut off my left pinky.

258
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:12,370
It won’t stop me
from using my sword, shooting.

259
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,800
or drawing a bow.

260
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,220
There, there.

261
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:32,430
It’s just a finger.

262
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,140
I’d rather die

263
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:41,090
than watch them hurting you.

264
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:51,030
Yan Xun.

265
00:14:01,060 --> 00:14:02,580
