266
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:05,110
We captured the one

267
00:14:05,110 --> 00:14:06,110
who murdered Mr. Luo

268
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:07,440
but the murderer already died.

269
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:08,890
There were two groups of people

270
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:09,640
fighting outside just now.

271
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,950
I didn’t even know the reason.

272
00:14:10,950 --> 00:14:11,730
Are the prisoners all right?

273
00:14:11,730 --> 00:14:12,580
They were fine

274
00:14:12,580 --> 00:14:14,010
until Young Master Zhao Xifeng came.

275
00:14:14,010 --> 00:14:15,460
He wanted to cut off that woman’s hand.

276
00:14:15,970 --> 00:14:16,810
Then what happened?

277
00:14:17,770 --> 00:14:18,930
His Excellency stopped him.

278
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:20,100
He cut off

279
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,270
his own finger instead.

280
00:14:24,650 --> 00:14:25,580
Young Master Yue.

281
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,090
Young Master Yue.

282
00:14:54,650 --> 00:14:55,740
How are you?

283
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:57,810
Still breathing.

284
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:03,970
Yan Xun…

285
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:05,220
Say no more.

286
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:08,120
I have one question for you.

287
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,590
When I tried to flee the city,

288
00:15:16,910 --> 00:15:18,800
someone shot me at the last minute.

289
00:15:20,980 --> 00:15:22,870
Was it your Ice Arrow?

290
00:15:26,100 --> 00:15:27,010
Yes.

291
00:15:32,330 --> 00:15:33,630
His Majesty ordered you

292
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,640
