293
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:36,920
of my father’s rebellion.

294
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:39,480
Was it true?

295
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:41,810
Yes.

296
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:52,130
When Zhao Dongting escorted my mother
back to Yanbei,

297
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:55,310
he made a detour to Jiangbei Camp

298
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:58,020
and brought 50 thousand soldiers with him.

299
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,150
You knew that, too?

300
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,110
Yes.

301
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:05,230
You knew His Majesty

302
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:07,210
intended to kill my father long ago?

303
00:16:18,130 --> 00:16:18,800
Yan Xun,

304
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,960
I kept giving you hints.

305
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:26,180
That day

306
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:30,990
on the Jiuyou Platform
before the execution,

307
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:35,310
did you think about those so-called hints?

308
00:16:37,830 --> 00:16:40,160
We have been friends for ten years!

309
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:48,860
All my family members’ lives

310
00:16:48,860 --> 00:16:50,510
were on the line.

311
00:16:52,370 --> 00:16:55,100
All you could do was dropping hints?

312
00:17:01,570 --> 00:17:02,800
Did you steal the letter from

313
00:17:03,190 --> 00:17:05,390
Marquis Dingbei to Yan Xun

314
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:06,600
and give it to His Majesty?

315
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:09,550
How did you know?

316
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,060
Yuwen Yue.

317
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:18,600
I don’t have

318
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,440
a friend like you.

319
00:17:25,110 --> 00:17:26,070
Just go.

320
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,910
If someone comes to see them again,

321
00:17:44,910 --> 00:17:46,540
report to Young Master immediately.

322
00:17:46,540 --> 00:17:47,860
Provide them

323
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:49,150
with all the necessary medicine and food.

324
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:51,270
If anything

325
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,650
happens to His Excellency Yan again,

326
00:17:52,650 --> 00:17:53,580
you will be the one

327
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:54,220
to blame.

328
00:17:55,020 --> 00:17:56,420
Yes, sir.

329
00:17:56,420 --> 00:17:58,260
I understand, sir.

330
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:01,570
They fought for one hour

331
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:02,820
with casualties on both sides.

332
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:05,120
After Cavalrymen arrived,

333
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,330
some of them escaped.

334
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,380
The state office took over the corpses.

335
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:10,990
They were all new faces.

336
00:18:11,510 --> 00:18:13,110
Based on their weapons

337
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,270
and skills,

338
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:17,010
they were more likely from the underworld.

339
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:19,500
We are still investigating

340
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,350
the cause of the fight

341
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:22,020
in front of the Imperial Prison.

342
00:18:30,290 --> 00:18:31,830
Is that necessary?

343
00:18:37,110 --> 00:18:38,960
That Prison is heavily guarded.

344
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,320
How could civilians

345
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:41,670
be anywhere near it?

346
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,630
Song.

347
00:18:47,910 --> 00:18:49,570
You really don’t know

348
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:52,910
or you are just playing dumb?

349
00:18:53,730 --> 00:18:54,750
I wouldn’t dare.

350
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:00,070
You are kindhearted.

351
00:19:00,730 --> 00:19:02,040
I don’t blame you.

352
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:05,900
There is one thing you need
to understand though.

353
00:19:06,340 --> 00:19:07,440
You should make friends

354
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,160
with the right people.

355
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:11,200
Yan Xun’s family members

356
00:19:11,410 --> 00:19:12,800
are convicted as rebels.

357
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:14,900
Making friends with the enemy

358
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:19,000
will eventually harm yourself
and those around you.

359
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,250
I am so sorry.

360
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:28,000
All that doesn’t matter right now.

361
00:19:28,310 --> 00:19:29,810
What matters is

362
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:32,350
Yan Shicheng’s accomplices

363
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,320
are still fighting against us.

364
00:19:35,080 --> 00:19:36,690
Places we have conquered

365
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:38,350
need to be governed.

366
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:42,410
Song, can you do that for me?

367
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:45,660
Father.

368
00:19:46,740 --> 00:19:48,620
You are assigning me
to govern those places?

369
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:51,250
I…

370
00:19:58,260 --> 00:19:59,270
Never mind.

371
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:02,270
You are too soft-hearted

372
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:05,000
with no understanding of the military.

373
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:07,400
Also,

374
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,520
you lack political practice.

375
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:13,850
If only Che were here,

376
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:17,460
he’d be the best choice.

377
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:21,000
How about

378
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,240
calling him back?

379
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:30,760
Father, Luo Yongchen is dead.

380
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,870
Should we find someone to take his place?

381
00:20:33,820 --> 00:20:35,170
That can wait.

382
00:20:38,190 --> 00:20:39,220
Father,

383
00:20:39,950 --> 00:20:41,240
I’ll take my leave then.

384
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,010
Father hasn’t appointed anyone

385
00:21:09,010 --> 00:21:10,200
to replace Mr. Luo.

386
00:21:12,670 --> 00:21:13,740
Maybe he can’t find the

387
00:21:13,740 --> 00:21:14,560
right person.

388
00:21:14,670 --> 00:21:16,090
Can’t find

389
00:21:16,090 --> 00:21:17,370
the right person?

390
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:19,440
He wants the Prison

391
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:20,920
to be leaderless.

392
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:22,710
He’s sending a message

393
00:21:22,870 --> 00:21:24,550
and telling everyone

394
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,650
he never means

395
00:21:25,650 --> 00:21:26,870
to remit Yan Xun’s death.

396
00:21:27,120 --> 00:21:28,300
Whoever hates him

397
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,490
can take this chance

398
00:21:29,490 --> 00:21:30,030
to do whatever...

399
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:30,840
Chun!

400
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,100
Do not judge father.

401
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,150
But that’s what he’s doing!

402
00:21:35,150 --> 00:21:35,790
Chun!

403
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:42,480
Brother, Yan Xun

404
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:43,680
has suffered too much.

405
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,720
Why is father

406
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,850
treating him like this?

407
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:48,610
Every time I close my eyes,

408
00:21:49,110 --> 00:21:50,170
what happened on Jiuyou Platform

409
00:21:50,170 --> 00:21:52,530
flashes back again and again.

410
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,890
It’s killing me,

411
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,910
not to mention Yan Xun.

412
00:21:57,810 --> 00:21:59,230
Can you imagine

413
00:21:59,690 --> 00:22:02,840
how desperate he is?

414
00:22:20,540 --> 00:22:26,060
= Imperial Prison =

415
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,010
You are awake.

416
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,390
Are you thirsty?

417
00:22:59,390 --> 00:23:00,610
I’ll get you some water.

418
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:15,990
Slowly.

419
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:22,440
Drink it.

420
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,990
You haven’t had anything the whole day.

421
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:39,780
You must be hungry.

422
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:42,470
I’m fine.

423
00:23:48,410 --> 00:23:50,190
Jailer, jailer!

424
00:23:50,190 --> 00:23:51,250
What’s up?

425
00:23:52,230 --> 00:23:53,190
What’s wrong?

426
00:23:54,450 --> 00:23:55,640
His Excellency has woken up?

427
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,520
Do you have any food?

428
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:57,570
Yes, yes.

429
00:23:58,030 --> 00:23:59,850
Master Yuwen Yue has asked me

430
00:24:00,130 --> 00:24:01,580
to provide you

431
00:24:01,580 --> 00:24:02,250
with enough food.

432
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,080
Wait a minute.

433
00:24:33,970 --> 00:24:34,620
Here.

434
00:24:39,710 --> 00:24:40,970
Your Excellency, your food.

435
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:42,970
Here you are.

436
00:24:42,970 --> 00:24:44,560
Feel free to tell me whatever you need.

437
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:45,240
Thank you.

438
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:46,880
You are welcome. I’m leaving.

439
00:24:59,020 --> 00:25:01,290
Here, drink it.

440
00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:13,030
Achu.

441
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,210
Have you eaten?

442
00:25:17,770 --> 00:25:18,750
I’m not hungry.

443
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:30,030
Eat something

444
00:25:30,530 --> 00:25:32,320
or you’ll get sick.

445
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:53,400
Is it good?

446
00:25:54,350 --> 00:25:55,130
Yes.

447
00:25:58,860 --> 00:25:59,750
Achu,

448
00:26:02,430 --> 00:26:04,190
I meant to take you back to Yanbei

449
00:26:04,910 --> 00:26:06,500
to give you a good life,

450
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:09,240
but unexpectedly,

451
00:26:09,910 --> 00:26:11,040
I had you

452
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:12,710
caged with me.

453
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:15,710
I’m sorry.

454
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:20,970
I’ll never

455
00:26:20,970 --> 00:26:22,310
promise you anything again.

456
00:26:24,520 --> 00:26:25,930
I’ll get you out

457
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:28,880
if I have the chance.

458
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:33,540
Yan Xun,

459
00:26:34,810 --> 00:26:36,320
when you were the prince,

460
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:38,380
I never looked up at you.

461
00:26:39,270 --> 00:26:40,660
Now that you are in trouble,

462
00:26:41,250 --> 00:26:43,070
I wouldn’t look down on you, either.

463
00:26:46,050 --> 00:26:47,710
I want to be your friend

464
00:26:47,950 --> 00:26:49,800
not because of your identity

465
00:26:50,190 --> 00:26:51,750
but because of who you are.

466
00:27:00,980 --> 00:27:02,040
And,

467
00:27:02,420 --> 00:27:03,750
I don’t think being here

468
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:04,560
is too bad.

469
00:27:05,390 --> 00:27:07,870
See? We have food
and a roof over our heads.

470
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:09,230
We are still alive.

471
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,260
I believe

472
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:15,760
you’ll get back on your feet someday.

473
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:20,350
I’ll have to rely on you

474
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:21,400
to live a well-off life.

475
00:27:28,130 --> 00:27:31,190
What should I do

476
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,640
once we arrive at Yanbei?

477
00:27:35,290 --> 00:27:36,570
To teach martial arts?

478
00:27:38,070 --> 00:27:39,130
I can throw punches.

479
00:27:40,930 --> 00:27:41,620
Wait,

480
00:27:42,450 --> 00:27:44,290
I don’t want to fight anymore.

481
00:27:45,290 --> 00:27:46,470
And you told me

482
00:27:46,870 --> 00:27:48,560
Yanbei is peaceful.

483
00:27:49,180 --> 00:27:50,850
People there can choose their lives.

484
00:27:53,570 --> 00:27:54,410
Didn’t you say

485
00:27:54,410 --> 00:27:56,010
we could hunt horses in Xiuli Mountain?

486
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,490
We can breed horses.

487
00:27:59,970 --> 00:28:03,140
I’ll be on the horseback

488
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:04,820
followed by thousands of cavalrymen.

489
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:05,800
How cool will that be!

490
00:28:06,630 --> 00:28:07,900
If anyone lays a finger on me,

491
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:09,520
you can have your men beat him.

492
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:10,780
I can finally be a bully

493
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:12,020
instead of being bullied.

494
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:14,620
= Imperial Prison =

495
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:34,370
Fool, fool!

496
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:36,810
Fool, fool!

497
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:42,030
Xing’er, Xing’er!

498
00:28:42,730 --> 00:28:44,790
Xing’er, Xing’er!

499
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:18,980
= Imperial Prison =

500
00:29:20,230 --> 00:29:23,150
Someone is protecting Yan Xun in secret?

501
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:24,140
Yes.

502
00:29:26,090 --> 00:29:27,460
Do you know who that is?

503
00:29:28,820 --> 00:29:29,850
Not yet.

504
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:31,780
I’ve sent men to check it.

505
00:29:34,320 --> 00:29:37,100
As requested, Ministry of Personnel

506
00:29:37,100 --> 00:29:37,930
has assembled all officials’ files,

507
00:29:37,930 --> 00:29:40,520
including their assessments, evaluations

508
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:42,270
and their backgrounds and resumes

509
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:43,510
over the past three years

510
00:29:43,510 --> 00:29:44,860
for Your Majesty to review.

511
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:49,900
Is there a candidate

512
00:29:50,850 --> 00:29:52,380
for Yanbei?

513
00:29:54,810 --> 00:29:56,140
Zhao Gui’s son,

514
00:29:56,140 --> 00:29:57,470
General Zhao Dongting,

515
00:29:57,470 --> 00:29:59,230
has potentials.

516
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:03,130
He’s a killer, but not a governor.

517
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:06,900
Wei Guang’s nephew, Wei Shuye,

518
00:30:07,450 --> 00:30:08,830
is loyal and diligent.

519
00:30:09,120 --> 00:30:10,800
He is outstanding

520
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:12,140
among his peers.

521
00:30:13,250 --> 00:30:16,540
Too weak-minded to shoulder the weight.

522
00:30:18,230 --> 00:30:20,070
Prince Jing’s heir Jing Han

523
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:23,420
is wise and capable.

524
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:28,090
Aren’t there any talents

525
00:30:28,420 --> 00:30:30,210
other than those

526
00:30:30,490 --> 00:30:32,060
from noble families

527
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:36,070
in our state?

528
00:30:36,650 --> 00:30:38,420
Li Xian, Governor of Jizhou,

529
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:41,470
rose from a commoner and he’s insightful.

530
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,810
It’s just that he is a bit old.

531
00:30:44,810 --> 00:30:46,290
He has turned 56.

532
00:30:49,690 --> 00:30:51,030
The old are more prudent

533
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:53,750
than the young.

534
00:30:54,560 --> 00:30:55,560
The age is not

535
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:56,930
a problem.

536
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:06,180
= Li Xian =

