00:31:07,050 --> 00:31:09,000
Assistant Chief of Guards, Jiang Wei,

538
00:31:09,230 --> 00:31:10,930
who used to serve

539
00:31:10,930 --> 00:31:12,370
under General of Chariots, Yang Mingqi,

540
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:14,650
is quite battlewise,

541
00:31:14,650 --> 00:31:17,020
cautious and erudite.

542
00:31:17,020 --> 00:31:18,780
He is a rare scholarly general.

543
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:21,150
But he’s of humble birth

544
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:23,740
as he was Yang Mingqi’s servant.

545
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,850
If he really is capable,

546
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:31,840
his birth will not be a problem.

547
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:34,710
Yes, Your Majesty.

548
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:38,090
Governor of Zhuzhou

549
00:31:38,210 --> 00:31:39,860
started as a scholar,

550
00:31:40,090 --> 00:31:41,260
but he’s well-versed
in military strategies.

551
00:31:41,430 --> 00:31:43,160
He has led villagers

552
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,470
to repulse the roving bandits many times.

553
00:31:44,470 --> 00:31:46,080
He is a doer.

554
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:54,610
The court

555
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:57,060
is filled with talkers.

556
00:31:58,230 --> 00:32:00,450
Doers are just what we need.

557
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:04,490
You’re a good judge of talent,
Your Majesty.

558
00:32:04,490 --> 00:32:06,100
Under your leadership,

559
00:32:06,100 --> 00:32:07,340
they can make full use of their talents

560
00:32:07,340 --> 00:32:08,620
to serve the state.

